Anyfesto set up installed on 10/2015. Aside from a few reboots for updates it has been running steady since.
FM broadcast is being handled by an external perspnal fm transmiter that covers the house and a bit.
A 1TB drive holds  
  -months worth of old time radio, talk and podcasts that are randomly played
  -a grab of PG and several other ebook collections
  -all the web site files.
  
  
